---

<div class="page-migrated page-musik-sv">
  <section class="content-section align-left">
    <div class="content-section-body">
      <h1>Music from <span class="brand-wordmark">ANDETAG</span></h1>
      <p>
        Music is a central part of <span class="brand-wordmark">ANDETAG</span>.<br />A slow rhythm.
        A shared breath.
      </p>
      <p>
        Here you find the album heard in the exhibition in Stockholm. Twelve tracks. Just over an hour
        of continuous listening. Music made to inhabit a space, rather than fill it.
      </p>
      <p>
        The compositions are created by Gustaf Tadaa and
        <a href="https://povelolsson.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><b>Povel Olsson</b></a>.
        The sound moves between piano and flute, electronic textures, and quiet field recordings. A
        passing train. Wind in the trees outside the house where the music took shape. The everyday,
        listened to slowly.
      </p>
      <p>
        Each track unfolds as its own story.<br />A movement between approach and resistance. Tension
        and release. Not to lead somewhere else, but to remain with what is.
      </p>
      <p>
        The music is made for listening.<br />At home. In headphones. In a room where time is allowed to
        slow down.
      </p>
      <p>
        <span class="brand-wordmark">ANDETAG</span> is available on
        <a
          href="https://open.spotify.com/album/16JNuKeBQUK3RZHQjj4nDV?si=nWPhkTpmRKKTFDhi3GBQsQ"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">Spotify</a>,
        <a
          href="https://music.apple.com/se/album/andetag/1843599465"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">Apple Music</a>,
        <a href="https://soundcloud.com/andetag" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Soundcloud</a>
        and
        <a href="https://andetagmuseum.bandcamp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bandcamp</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="embed-shell page-musik-sv__spotify" aria-label="Spotify">
    <iframe
      title="ANDETAG on Spotify"
      src={spotifyEmbedSrc}
      width="100%"
      height="652"
      class="embed-frame page-musik-sv__spotify-frame"
      loading="lazy"
      allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
      referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
    />
  </section>
</div>
